Path: Looking ahead
Content:
We're hard at work on the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/261] upcoming milestone release
. If you'd like to help, feel free to jump in! We have an active 
[link: https://discord.gg/NtAbbGn] discord
 you can join for both users and contributors.
